Package: solaR2
Type: Package
Title: Radiation and Photovoltaic Systems
Version: 0.11
Encoding: UTF-8
Authors@R: c(person("Oscar", "Perpiñán-Lamigueiro",
        email="oscar.perpinan@upm.es", role="aut", comment = c(ORCID =
        "0000-0002-4134-7196")), person("Francisco", "Delgado-López",
        email="f.delgadol@alumnos.upm.es", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides tools for calculating solar geometry, solar
        radiation on horizontal and inclined planes, and simulating the
        performance of various photovoltaic (PV) systems. Supports
        daily and intradaily irradiation data, enabling detailed
        analysis of grid-connected and water-pumping PV systems,
        including shading effects and solar angle calculations.
URL: https://solarization.github.io/solaR2/
BugReports: https://github.com/solarization/solaR2/issues
License: GPL-3
